{"article_id":"hdGqXF93QTCKtL5f","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Republican lawmakers are breathing a sigh of relief","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"that the Trump administration backed away from seeking an immediate repeal of the Affordable Care Act","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"without a replacement plan ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"and instead will take the issue on the 2020 campaign trail .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"`` I was disappointed","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"when we were talking about repeal","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"only without a credible plan","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"to replace , ''","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"Indiana Sen. Mike Braun","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"( R )","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"told News .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"`` We need to now as conservatives start talking about what are we going to do . ''","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"President Trump surprised many in his own party","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"when he declared","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"that Republicans would be the party of health care ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"prompting Majority Leader Mitch McConnell to tell him this week","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"he had no plans","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"of taking up comprehensive health care reform with a Democratic-controlled House .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"`` I made clear to him","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"that we were not going to be doing that in the Senate , ''","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"McConnell told reporters .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"`` He did say ,","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"as he later tweeted ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"that he accepted that","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"and he would be developing a plan","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"that he would take to the American people during the 2020 campaign . ''","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"McConnell says","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"he wants Senate Republicans focusing on bills","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"to keep health care costs down , not comprehensive replacement plans","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"and Sen. Braun agrees .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"`` I think","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"the right decision was made","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"to make sure","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"we get our ducks in a row ,","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"throw the onus on the industry in the meantime ,","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"have senators and congressmen","depth":16},{"id":36,"text":"that know a little bit about it like me","depth":16},{"id":37,"text":"to start prodding the industry ,","depth":15},{"id":38,"text":"because I think","depth":15},{"id":39,"text":"it 's going to take more than their own self-correction , ''","depth":15},{"id":40,"text":"Braun told News .","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"Braun described his own issues","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"dealing with health insurance companies","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"while trying to find a plan for his employers .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"`` It was like pulling teeth","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"to get the solution ,","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"that they had the nerve","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"to say","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"you 're lucky","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"it 's only going up 5 % this year and then 10 % next year ,","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"I found a way","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"to solve that , ''","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"said Braun .","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"And he calls out his own party for being longtime `` apologists for health care , ''","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"adding","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"it 's time","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"for Republicans to come up with their own solutions to the growing costs .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"`` I think","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"all Hoosiers , Americans are frustrated with health care","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"as it 's being delivered by a so-called free market industry .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"The fact is it 's not ,","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"its got highly concentrated","depth":14},{"id":62,"text":"with big companies running the show","depth":14},{"id":63,"text":"and I think","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"its incumbent on the industry","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"if it does n't want one business partner with the federal government to start doing a better job , ''","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"said Braun .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"`` I am going to try and help promote that through price transparency bills , bills","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"that would take generics from discussion to the marketplace more quickly , those kinds of things . ''","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Braun told President Trump","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"he 'd work with him on a replacement plan","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"but is glad they have time","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"to think through it .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"`` As long as that does n't mean we 're going to lay low","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"and let the Democrats kind of control the dialogue , ''","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"continued Braun .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"`` What I 'm going to do is work on lowering the cost ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"making it more transparent","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"and take that approach .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"Somewhere down the road , it 's going to be the alternative","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"that the other side is offering","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"which sounds so enticing . ''","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"`` Medicare for all , I think","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"we 'd regret it","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"because first of all it costs so much already ,","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"running deficits to where we do n't pay for the government","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"we 're already demanding , ''","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"he explained .","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"`` So I think","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"they 've got a lot","depth":15},{"id":90,"text":"that we can hit","depth":15},{"id":91,"text":"to where how 's that going to work ?","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"It 's not going to pan out .","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"On the other hand , we 've got to devise a system","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"if we want to save the system .","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"It 's got to shrink .","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"It 's got to get better .","depth":15},{"id":97,"text":"It 's got to offer us better value .","depth":15},{"id":98,"text":"That means to solve the problems","depth":15},{"id":99,"text":"and lower the prices . ''","depth":15},{"id":100,"text":"But Democrats say","depth":4},{"id":101,"text":"Republicans have no health care plan of their own .","depth":4},{"id":102,"text":"`` The president tweeted","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"that they will come up with their plan in 2021 .","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"Translation :","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"they have no health care plan .","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"It 's the same old song","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"they 've been singing ,","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"they 're for repeal ,","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"they have no replace , ''","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"said Minority Leader Chuck Schumer","depth":5},{"id":111,"text":"( D-NY ) .","depth":5},{"id":112,"text":"News Political Analyst David Brody discusses President Trump 's ideas for health care and the southern border on Tuesday 's The 700 Club .","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":225,"left":224,"right":112,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":224,"left":212,"right":223,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":124,"right":211,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":116,"right":123,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":0,"right":115,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":114,"right":3,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":114,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"pa